            "type": "text",
            "text": "The Qwen3 TTS 12Hz 1.7B VoiceDesign model delivers advanced text-to-speech capabilities with a 12Hz sampling rate and 1.7 billion parameters, enabling high-quality audio synthesis. This guide offers actionable steps for experienced API teams to integrate and optimize this model in production systems."
