            "type": "text",
            "text": "The model leverages a transformer-based architecture optimized for real-time audio generation. Key metrics include a latency under 200ms for short texts and support for multiple voice designs via customizable embeddings. Ensure your infrastructure handles the 12Hz output rate efficiently to avoid bottlenecks."
